title: 08/16/21 DPS Hour 2 Warren Sharp
itunes:title: 08/16/21 DPS Hour 2 Warren Sharp
description:
Doug Gottlieb and Rob Parker, in for Dan, discuss the new crop of rookie quarterback and react to the ones who made the biggest impressions in their preseason debuts. Doug and Rob debate some of the biggest moments of Tom Brady's career. Warren Sharp of Sharp Football Analysis joins the guys to look at what impact Matt Stafford should make for the Rams. Plus, Rob tells Doug why he is not a believer in Stafford despite his change of scenery.
